OL,4,Ctransplants 'forever grateful' to
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,FA father of two who had four liver
OL,8,Ftransplants before the age of 30 has
OL,9,Fsaid he "can't thank the donors
OL,10,Fenough" for giving him the chance to
OL,11,Fsee his children grow up.
OL,13,FMartin Dillett, who lives in Broxburn
OL,14,Fnear Edinburgh with his wife and two
OL,15,Fyoung daughters, had his first liver
OL,16,Ftransplant when he was just three
OL,17,Fyears old after being diagnosed with a
OL,18,Frare liver disease.
OL,26,@qD@IOUrD@GO]
