OL,3,CFather of two who has had four liver
OL,4,Ctransplants 'forever grateful' to
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,F"All the toxins that your liver is
OL,8,Fmeant to clear out of your body, it
OL,9,Fwasn't doing that."
OL,11,FHe explained this led to him
OL,12,Fexperiencing episodes of hepatic
OL,13,Fencephalopathy (a decline in brain
OL,14,Ffunction caused by toxins in the
OL,15,Fblood), jaundice, constant itchiness,
OL,16,Fweight loss and a failing pancreas.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@SO]
