OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,FAfter periods in and out of hospital,
OL,8,Fin August 2023 Mr Dillett's liver went
OL,9,Finto full failure and he was rushed to
OL,10,Fthe Royal Infirmary of Edinburgh
OL,11,F(RIE), where he was moved to intensive
OL,12,Fcare while doctors waited for a liver
OL,13,Fto become available.
OL,15,FMr Dillett's wife Danielle, who was
OL,16,Fexpecting her second child at the
OL,17,Ftime, recalled that at this stage: "We
OL,18,Fwere really getting to a life-or-death
OL,19,Fsituation and time was ticking on.
OL,26,@yD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
