OL,3,CFather of two who has had four liver
OL,4,Ctransplants 'forever grateful' to
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,F"Each day it became more likely he
OL,8,Fwould be put into an induced coma."
OL,10,FAfter 11 days in hospital a liver was
OL,11,Ffound, but even though the operation
OL,12,Fto transplant it was successful the
OL,13,Forgan itself was not functioning, so
OL,14,FMr Dillett was put back on the
OL,15,Ftransplant waiting list.
OL,17,FThe following day another liver was
OL,18,Ffound and, 48 hours after his previous
OL,19,Ftransplant, he was again taken into
OL,20,Fthe operating theatre.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@cO]
