OL,4,Ctransplants 'forever grateful' to
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,FHowever, this new liver also failed to
OL,8,Ffunction, and Mrs Dillett said she got
OL,9,Fa phone call from the hospital telling
OL,10,Fher to "get to the hospital
OL,11,Fimmediately as the new liver still
OL,12,Fwasn't working and Martin's body was
OL,13,Fshutting down".
OL,15,FShe continued: "Doctors told me his
OL,16,Fsituation was critical and his full
OL,17,Fteam agreed to go back into surgery to
OL,18,Fsee if they could reroute the portal
OL,19,Fvein, but they advised it may not work.
OL,26,@rD@HOUuD@NO]wD@POU
