OL,3,CFather of two who has had four liver
OL,4,Ctransplants 'forever grateful' to
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,F"I was just lucky that the consultants
OL,8,Fand the surgeons and everybody kept
OL,9,Fgoing and kept fighting to keep me
OL,10,Falive," he said.
OL,12,F"And luckily enough, my body withstood
OL,13,Fall the medication and the stress it
OL,14,Fwas under to be well enough to be
OL,15,Ftransplanted."
OL,17,FMr Dillett added that he hoped his
OL,18,Fstory will inspire more people to
OL,19,Fbecome organ donors.
