OL,3,CFather of two who has had four liver
OL,4,Ctransplants 'forever grateful' to
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,F"I can't thank the donors enough for
OL,8,Fthat, and anybody that is on the
OL,9,Ffence, I think hearing stories like
OL,10,Fmine, and a lot of people's stories,
OL,11,Fwould definitely help to convince
OL,12,Fthem."
OL,14,FMrs Dillett described donating an
OL,15,Forgan as an "incredible gift".
OL,17,F"I hope our story shows how much organ
OL,18,Fdonation can change people's lives,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
