OL,3,CFather of two who has had four liver
OL,4,Ctransplants 'forever grateful' to
OL,5,Cdonors
OL,7,F"During the darkest time, knowing
OL,8,Fthere were organ donors out there gave
OL,9,Fus hope that things might be OK. We
OL,10,Fthink about Martin's donors all the
OL,11,Ftime and are forever grateful for
OL,12,Ftheir incredible gift."
OL,14,FOrgan and Tissue Donation Week runs
OL,15,Ffrom September 23-29, and aims to
OL,16,Fremind people to make their choices
OL,17,Fabout organ donation known, and not to
OL,18,Fleave their loved ones in doubt.
